     SHORT="pop3share is a file server that uses the POP3 protocol for transfers."
      LONG="
It was developed to dodge the filesharing radar of your ISP, 
your boss, or whomever may be interested in what you're sharing.
It requires no client software besides a mail client, 
and most clients should work.
